data.description: Fabulous true ranch home with 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths!  Great room has beautiful fireplace, vaulted ceiling and opens to the dining/kitchen.  The kitchen features gorgeous painted cabinets, granite counters, stainless appliances (fridge stays), pantry closet and wood floors!  Primary bedroom has walk-in closet plus full bath.  Two additional bedrooms on main level plus full bath.  The laundry room is conveniently located by kitchen and garage entrance with washer/dryer staying.  Walkout lower level offers a ton more living space with a cozy family room area, plus a large rec room!  There's also a 4th bedroom and 3rd full bath!  Fenced backyard with deck that overlooks garden beds and playset that stays.  Covered front porch with a nice culdesac view.  Roof 5 1/2 yrs, HVAC under 4 yrs!  Sugarland community offers ponds and walking trails!
